overnment ministers, as part of the recent crackdown. The group has seen renewed activity in recent months, though violence has continued. They plan to meet again in June, this time with Arab representatives in the Middle East. The Quartet produced the stalled road map peace plan that was to culminate with statehood for the Palestinians. From French fries to calamari rings to health food, the Taste of the City Festival has it all. Comme il faut embarks on a new approach to fashion this summer, gimmicks intact. Egypt`s right. It`s not just Pals. Other Arabs share the blame As if Egypt really cares... it is time to become honest with egypt and their war against us Who is to blame? Egypt losing credibility fast with one-sided support for Hamas Dont ever blame the palis Egypt crap and the world of the dark forces like Egypt has any credibility yes , it is blatant double standards Egypt is quite right about the Quartet`s bias quartet is immoral group Palestinian: the old "murderer or children" accusation Remove all Pali Arab Occupiers Egypt is our Peace by Peace partner More proof main problem is Egypt violates its treaty with Israel 19Barry,you sound like a pretty ignorant fellow,you should stay # 14 Hamas is totally unethical Not all Moslems are terrorist, but Hamas IS Terrorist # 2 On Egypt caring Our friends, the Egyptians Look where it`s coming from... Bradley Burston: Boycotting Israel as moral masturbation Amira Hass: Israel waging technological war on Palestinians Talia Sasson: Forcing Israeli Arabs to take a loyalty oath South Africa's largest trade union seeks to boycott Israel U.K. minister slams British boycott of Israeli academic institutions Olmert explores, via third party, resuming talks with Syria * Thompson warns: Israel might attack Iran * It's not the war stupid, it's the occupation * Guest: Going to shul is not cool? * Revisiting the possibility of a Rice ticket in 2008 U.K. public services union to weigh boycott of Israel Officials: Israel ready to 